body.name: RASOO Bathroom Storage Cabinet White Freestanding Floor Storage Cupboard Adjustable Shelf with 4 Drawers and 1 Door
features: High Quality Material : Our RASOO Bathroom cabinet constructed by P2 grade MDF board. It features solidity and durability . The medium density fiberboard won't be affected with damp and won't deform after years of using. And painted by the upgraded UV, it is more scratch resistant.

More Space: Finished with a contemporary White-colored handle, 4 slatted drawers design with routed handles, suitable place for family sized bottles. The cabinet door houses an adjustable shelf to customize your storage space.

Versatile Function: It is suitable as bathroom floor cabinet for keeping your bathroom clutter free, four deep drawers and a cupboard to conceal towels, toiletries and other essentials. And it also can be used as storage cabinet or sideboard, makes your room tidy and clean.

Easy matching: The Bathroom storage cabinet is modern in white. It is perfect for any house style, like living room, bathroom, hallway, study or office, and also easy matching with any type of furniture.

Excellent Warranty and After Sales Service: Free replacement or money back for quality issues within 30 days, Lifetime warranty on accessories. Customer satisfaction has always been our pursuit, if you are unhappy with our products, please do not hesitate to contact us for help. Overall size: 22.05"X 11.81"X 32.68"（L x W x H）（Please check the size carefully before purchase）.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy and useful
reviews.reviewText: These are a quality product. Good assembly instructions as well. Put one together in a half hour. Very sturdy and has held up well over the last year. Drawers provide adequate space and the cabinet side has adjustable shelves to fit your needs. Great value for a good cabinet.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Ease of assembly
reviews.reviewText: It's a good size to fit in the bathroom. It took a about an hour to set it up. It's easy to set up as follow the instructions. Four drawers and a cabinet can hold a lot of stuff. Like it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 3, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Precision Cut / Fit (press board)
reviews.reviewText: You get what you pay for. I believe all these cabinets in this price range would be of this quality, so no surprises here.UPDATE: After assembling this cabinet I raised the rating and would like to add that I'm impressed with the precision of all the components. With care and patience, it assembled seamless, perfect fit of all parts. All the panels were obviously CNC cut with tight tolerance. I added glue to all the dowels and it is super sturdy now. However, the press fiberboard is not durable.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 2, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect. Get it.
reviews.reviewText: Took my time assembling. Fairly easy. One part was difficult but I figured it out. Totally worth it. Perfect size for bathroom. Good quality. Looks nice, just as pictured. Not disappointed at all!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 3, 2023
reviews.reviewText: The height is perfect. The design is perfect. The color is perfect.The magnet that holds the doors is not great as the strength is weak; to mean one door will not hold latched to the magnet but just kinda "balances" there.Putting it together was a pain in the butt simply because the directions were overdone with do this - do that and it took almost 2 hours and I am a direction wiz.The drawers are not deep and that is okay but because they are short there is no balance for them when pulled out and that means you have to hold them or they will fall out. However, the stand itself is balanced and is level on the floor - no wobbles.The inside shelf is fine as all I have on it are DVDs. The pieces that are there to hold the shelf can be adjusted.Was it worth the money? No, not at all. At best it should be priced much lower.Will I keep it? Yes. For what I got it for it will simply do but if one is looking for something to constantly be in use in and out of then this stand/unit will make you quite grumpy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Worst drawer ever
reviews.reviewText: This is the crappiest drawer set I’ve ever had. Not worth it if you got it for free. It’s unstable and falls apart at the touch of a drawer. You can’t move it anywhere before it collapses. You can’t even screw any parts together because it’s not even scrap wood. This crap is made of cardboard paper or something because it just chips apart at any attempt to stabilize . I wish I could’ve retuned it but I missed the window and now I’m stuck with expensive trash
